import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import ButtonMarker from './'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"button-marker"}}>{`Button Marker`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={ButtonMarker} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={1} __code={`<ButtonMarker background="blue" label="Click me!" />`} __scope={{props,ButtonMarker}}>
  <ButtonMarker background="blue" label="Click me!" />
</Playground></MDXTag>
